DESCRIPTION:The Ballast on Salem is pleased to invite local vendors to par
 ticipate in our First Annual Summer Market. This community event is design
 ed to bring together residents and local businesses for an afternoon of sh
 opping\, networking\, and community engagement. This event will be hosted 
 onsite at our residential community and is an excellent opportunity to sho
 wcase your products and services to residents and guests. If you are inter
 ested in participating or would like additional information regarding vend
 or requirements\, space availability\, or setup details\, please contact u
 s at: theballastonsalem@greystar.com We look forward to connecting with lo
 cal vendors and making this inaugural event a success.
